ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 13th day of November, 2015, the Application for Leave to File Original Process and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus are GRANTED. The Court of Common Pleas of Philadelphia County is DIRECTED to dispose of Petitioner’s pending petition within 90 days. The Prothonota-ry is DIRECTED to strike the name of jurist from the caption.
